                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Montreal</placeName>\n                <date>21 Apl 65</date>.</p>\n            <p>The <addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir—</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I don't know whether<lb/> you understood that I expected<lb/> the\n                pamphlets (in paper wrappers)<lb/> without the Err<add>?</add>. In any<lb/> case\n                please send them on by<lb/> express. <persName>Mrs J H Joseph</persName> is<lb/> now\n                on a visit to your city<lb/> but the parcel would be too<lb/> large for her I fear\n                as she<lb/> takes but one small trunk,</p>"
                  },
